snippet.title: Awkward Dimensions Redux Gameplayey Trailer
snippet.description: A gameplay trailer full of gameplay because gameplay. Boy o' boy I do love me some guudd gameplay, coz thar aint no play like gameplay, a whole lotta gameplay, I think a game needs to be fun or its not a game, my opinion is limiting the room for creativity in the games medium, I love tripple AAA unoriginal pander and hate those indie scum, gameplay... gameplay... gameplay...
